reviewText: Awesome DVD. Love the new Rocksteady and Bebop!!!!

We've waited a long time for them, but your favorite bad guy mutant warthog and rhinoceros duo is back! Bebop (Anton Zeck) and Rocksteady (Ivan Steranko), new members of Shredder's henchmen, are on the scene and have a bone to pick with the Turtles.
I grew up with the TMNT so I thought to give a try with my kids. After the first episode we were all hooked up to the series!

The show still knows how to entertain the audience, I still kinda wish The Finger became Rocksteady instead, that guy was short enough and dumb enough to be a talking rhino mutant. Ivan Steranko had more to offer as a character as well, but I guess the developers didn't know what to do with a weapons dealer in a kids' show. Other than that, the series was (like I said) fantastic!
I love the series so I had to buy this one to add to  the family collection.

I bought this for my four year old son and he was really happy. He missed the episodes with bebop and rocksteady on Nick, so he is really happy to see them now. The price was great and shipping was fast. I would definitely buy again.

Growing up with the original TMNT cartoon in the 80s/90s, I'll admit I was first leary about this series. However, I gave it a shot and quickly enjoyed it. They pay homage to not only the original cartoon but also the comics and the first few movies from the early 90s. The shout-outs to the original series are awesome and the fact they incorporate some of the older characters is great. I bought all the DVD sets thus far of the Nickelodeon series at the store but this one I bought online the day it came out. My fiancee and I both watch this and we were anticipating this set. We were not disappointed and we're now eagerly anticipating the next set.
I was very impressed to get this item way before I expected!
